  "remarks": "Pursuant to paragraph 6 of Security Council Resolution 2371 (2017), paragraph 6 of Security Council Resolution 2375 (2017) and paragraph 12 of Security Council resolution 2321 (2016). M/V HAO FAN 2 loaded DPRK coal at Nampo, DPRK, on 3 June 2017, for export in violation of UN sanctions. Listed as asset of Shen Zhong International Shipping (OFSI ID: 13644, UN Reference Number: UN Ref KPe.073)",
